spx.packets

Class TrackerStatus

  • java.lang.Object
    • spx.packets.TrackerStatus

  • public class TrackerStatus
extends java.lang.Object
    Traker status message.

    This class is kept in sync with the C++ SPxPacketTrackerStatus_t structure from "SPxPackets.h".

    • Field Detail

      • reportType

        public long reportType
        Current track report type from tracker.

        The reportType field will contain one of the following constants from the Type interface:

        • NONE
        • TRACK_MIN
        • TRACK_NORM
        • TRACK_EXT
        See Also:
        Type

        public short flags
        Bitmask of which of the optional tracker status fields are present.

        The valid values for the bitmask are constants in the TrackerStatusFlags interface.

        See Also:
        TrackerStatusFlags
